name: Retell AI
headline: Supercharge Your Contact Center Operations with AI Phone Agents
description: The leading platform for building and managing AI voice agents that revolutionize contact center operations.

founders.name: Bing Wu, Founder
founders.description:
Co-founder & CEO at Retell AI.
Enthusiastic about the human brain and AI, Bing spent three years as a product manager at ByteDance/TikTok, where he led B2B and consumer products that delighted billions.

Before joining ByteDance/TikTok, Bing founded two investor-backed startups in college, generating six-figure revenues.

founders.name: Todd Li, Founder
founders.description: Todd is the founder of several venture-backed startups. Before his startup journey at Retell, Todd worked at Google Ads as a software engineer.

founders.name: Evie Wang, Founder
founders.description:
Evie is the Co-founder and CMO of Retell AI
She has a design background and a deep understanding of B2B business as she spent 3 years as a Product Designer at Bytedance.

founders.name: Weijia Yu, Founder
founders.description:
Weijia excels in product and software development, with a specialization in machine learning. At Meta, he spent three years as a PM hybrid Tech Lead within Facebook product team.

Prior to Meta, Weijia led app development at ObEN, a Series B AI tech startup, providing full-stack AI solutions including TTS(text-to-speech), computer vision and chatbot.

founders.name: Zexia Zhang, Founder
founders.description: Zexia is the co-founder and CTO of Retell AI. Passionate about ML, Zexia is always at the frontier of advancing speech technologies. Before Retell, Zexia spent four years at Google where he led the development of next-gen speech translation experience, and NLP solutions for call analysis.

F.A.Q
### Questions & answers
All account has a 60-minutes ($10) free trial.
How can I create a voice AI agent for my company?
Creating a voice AI agent with Retell is easy! Start by creating an account on the Retell dashboard. Each account comes with 60 minutes of free usage. Once logged in, you can build a voice agent and use our custom tools to integrate it with your company’s data seamlessly.
What is the pricing for Retell AI?
Retell AI offers a pay-as-you-go model starting at $0.07 per minute, depending on the selected voice and LLM configurations. We also offer an Enterprise Plan with reduced rates, custom concurrent call options, and premium support.
Can I connect the agent to my existing phone number?
Yes, you can! Retell supports integration with any telephony system through SIP trunking, making it easy to connect your existing phone number.
What resources does my company need to use Retell AI?
You’ll need one engineer to integrate Retell AI with your systems and create a voice AI agent. The initial setup typically takes anywhere from a few hours to a few days. Once the agent is set up, ongoing maintenance can be handled by a product manager or similar team member.
More questions? Visit our [docs](https://retellai.com/<https:/docs.retellai.com/general/introduction>)

F.A.Q
### Questions & answers
All account has a 60-minutes ($10) free trial.
How can I create a voice AI agent for my company?
Creating a voice AI agent with Retell is easy! Start by creating an account on the Retell dashboard. Each account comes with 60 minutes of free usage. Once logged in, you can build a voice agent and use our custom tools to integrate it with your company’s data seamlessly.
What is the pricing for Retell AI?
Retell AI offers a pay-as-you-go model starting at $0.07 per minute, depending on the selected voice and LLM configurations. We also offer an Enterprise Plan with reduced rates, custom concurrent call options, and premium support.
Can I connect the agent to my existing phone number?
Yes, you can! Retell supports integration with any telephony system through SIP trunking, making it easy to connect your existing phone number.
What resources does my company need to use Retell AI?
You’ll need one engineer to integrate Retell AI with your systems and create a voice AI agent. The initial setup typically takes anywhere from a few hours to a few days. Once the agent is set up, ongoing maintenance can be handled by a product manager or similar team member.

**Retell AI: Transforming Contact Center Operations with Voice AI**

Founded in 2023 and part of Y Combinator's Batch W24, Retell AI is already making waves in the field of artificial intelligence, particularly in the contact center industry. Their mission is clear: to supercharge contact center operations using AI phone agents. The company offers a state-of-the-art platform designed for building and managing AI voice agents, aiming to revolutionize how businesses handle customer interactions.

Located in the Bay Area, with a lean team of just five employees, Retell AI operates under the guidance of its Group Partner, Michael Seibel. The company’s innovative strides are aimed at addressing common pain points in customer service by utilizing AI technology to automate and enhance communication efficiency.

### **Key Features and Offerings**

Retell AI's platform boasts a suite of robust features designed to streamline contact center tasks:

- **Call Transfer and Appointment Booking:** Equipped with warm transfer capabilities and seamless integration with scheduling services like Cal.com, Retell AI ensures transitions from AI to human agents are smooth.
  
- **Knowledge Base Syncing:** The system can auto-sync with existing resources, keeping AI agents up-to-date without manual intervention.

- **IVR Navigation:** The AI can handle complex Interactive Voice Response systems, making it versatile in various scenarios.

- **Batch Calls:** Users can send masses of calls simultaneously, optimizing outreach without overwhelming their existing systems.

- **Customization and Monitoring:** The platform allows for post-call analysis and monitoring of agent performance, ensuring continuous improvement.

### **Industries Served**

Retell AI is tailored to serve a broad spectrum of industries, including:

- **Healthcare**
- **Financial Services**
- **Insurance**
- **Logistics**
- **Home Services**
- **Retail & Consumer Goods**
- **Travel & Hospitality**
- **Debt Collection**

### **Measurable Impact**

The early adopters of Retell AI's technology report impressive results:
For instance, Gifthealth achieved a **4x operational efficiency**, with 50% of calls resolved without human intervention. Similarly, Everise saved over **600 hours** of manpower monthly, showcasing the substantial productivity gains that can be realized through Retell’s AI solutions.

### **Get Started**

Retell AI offers a **60-minute free trial** for potential users, operating on a pay-as-you-go model with pricing beginning at just $0.07 per minute. This approach allows businesses to easily integrate Retell AI with existing technologies like Twilio and Vonage, or connect through SIP trunking to optimize their communication channels.

You can explore more about Retell AI and how to transform your contact center by visiting their website: [Retell AI](https://retellai.com).

In the customer service landscape where efficiency and customer satisfaction are paramount, Retell AI is not just an option; it’s becoming a necessity for businesses eager to leverage cutting-edge technology to enhance their operations.
